parser.visitor.myvisitor

Class PentaStaffCompilerVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.visitor.myvisitor.PentaStaffCompilerVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IVoidVisitor

    public class PentaStaffCompilerVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IVoidVisitor
    Visitor for staff writing. It gives no semantic check. Callable only after semantic check by PentaParseVisitor if it gives positive result. While parsing, it will write music only during the essay phase (sounds declared in strophes will only be written when strophes occurs in essay!)
    Author:
    Matteo Poggi
